Myra Kinch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Myra_Kinch 0 Myra Kinch (1904 - November 20, 1981) was a choreographer and dancer who appeared in several Hollywood motion pictures. She was from Los Angeles, California. Her eyes were blue and her hair was a dark red.
